      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, can you help me draft a job description for a Senior Accountant position? It's for our global firm. We need to make sure it mentions they need a CPA certification, experience with GAAP, and they have to be proficient in SAP. Just a standard professional layout is fine.",
